{"tid":701737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港未來人 林一鳴 十大經濟預言","createTime":"2018-06-14T10:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T23:47:42.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8a79944996eeaa381f3115a3047d9c113900f808","tid":701737,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:55:31.000Z","msg":"林一鳴於2008年出版了一本名為《猴子的戲法不靈了!?》的書，內有他對世界財經發展的「十大預言」，如下：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.美國評級下降，導致美元貶值。<br />\n2.中國外匯儲備部份以黃金取代美元美債。<br />\n3.世界部分國家重新考慮執行金本位制度。<br />\n4.金價大幅攀升逾每盎司2000美元。<br />\n5.商品牛市將持續10年以上，導致嚴重通脹。<br />\n6.投資銀行崔護重來，金融危機再現。<br />\n7.美國國債乏人問津，導致價格下降。<br />\n8.人民幣自由浮動，最終成為國際主要貨幣。<br />\n9.港元最終與人民幣掛勾。<br />\n10.中國崛起，成為世界經濟第一大國。"},{"pid":"f09d3e9bcf1820e130d80067f2f657bf03699815","tid":701737,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 專家"},{"pid":"1f7b3205d5aef28e9110b68853b24d57e8c03df1","tid":701737,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"新嘅燈神誕生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ee3bdbf077940501a5f2814d66a7589100768d","tid":701737,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"聽佢講就真係死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47630efc85b38991cff5c2a475750f3c4f3cdcc9","tid":701737,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a648c114024b139dfc4089c0f2bb54c19e60c2b","tid":701737,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T16:41:14.000Z","msg":"全部開對家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc39295557897758b8d56567fb93c3c05382727","tid":701737,"uid":104699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,